I"¸<p><strong>Mass and density functions</strong></p>

<p>Mass function</p>

<p>The probability mass function (p.m.f.) is the histogram of the
distribution, that is:</p>

<p>- x-axis: values</p>

<p>- y-axis: frequency</p>

<p>Density function</p>

<p>The probability density function (p.d.f.) is the "smooth histogram" of
the distribution.</p>

